ne)\n- Reads version from `.cloche/version`\n- Queries git history for prompt files in `.cloche/prompts/`\n- Returns JSON with: docker_image, version, prompt_files (with commit history)\n\n### 5. **.gitignore files**\n\n**Primary .gitignore:** `/workspace/.gitignore`\n- Ignores: `.env`, `bin/`, `.serena/`, Claude Code settings\n- Excludes built binaries: `/cloche`, `/cloched`, `/cloche-agent`\n- Excludes databases: `*.db`, `*.db-shm`, `*.db-wal`\n- Excludes runtime artifacts: `.cloche/*-*-*/`, `.cloche/run-*/`, `.cloche/attempt_count/`, `.gitworktrees/`\n- Tracks workflow and config files (not ignored): `.cloche/prompts/`, `.cloche/overrides/`, `.cloche/evolution/`\n- Excludes example projects' runtime state: `examples/*/.cloche/`\n\n**Secondary .gitignore:** `/workspace/.beads/.gitignore`\n- Handles daemon runtime files: `daemon.lock`, `daemon.log`, `daemon.pid`\n- Excludes databases and sync state\n- Protects against accidental commit of merge artifacts\n- Note: JSONL files (issues.jsonl, interactions.jsonl) are tracked by default\n\nAll file paths are absolute paths from `/workspace/`."}],"totalDurationMs":39922,"totalTokens":56512,"totalToolUseCount":16,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5465,"cache_read_input_tokens":49904,"output_tokens":1140,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5465},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
